HOUSE SUBSTITUTE FOR
SENATE BILL NO. 99
A bill to amend 2023 PA 281, entitled
"Public officers financial disclosure act,"
by amending sections 3, 5, 7, 8, 11, 13, and 15 (MCL 15.703,
15.705, 15.707, 15.708, 15.711, 15.713, and 15.715) and by adding
section 6.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
