13 Sec. 7. (1) A report required under section 5 must include a
14 complete statement of all of the following:
15 (a) The full name, mailing address, telephone number, and
16 email address of the public officer.
17 (b) The name and address of the public officer's employer or
18 employers and the positions held during the reporting period, if
19 the public officer receives $1,000.00 or more in annual income from
20 each position.
21 (c) The name of the spouse of the public officer ,and, if the
22 public officer's spouse receives $1,000.00 or more in annual
23 income, the occupation of the public officer's spouse , and the
24 name of the employer or employers of the public officer's spouse..
25 (d) Whether the public officer's spouse was registered as a
26 lobbyist or lobbyist agent under 1978 PA 472, MCL 4.411 to 4.431,
27 during the reporting period.
28 (e) A list of all positions currently held as an officer,
29 director, trustee, partner, proprietor, representative, employee,
